Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.63,0:22:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.78,0:23:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.47,0:23:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宫子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.21,0:23:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.35,0:23:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宫子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.77,0:23:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 亏你还记得我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.51,0:23:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直联系不上你 我好担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得手机开机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.57,0:23:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没有消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.22,0:23:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来我还没有消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.89,0:23:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不识愁滋味 只会迎来更大的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.60,0:23:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.42,0:23:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ef - a tale of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.76,0:23:41.34,Next,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp22.5}{\K140}勿忘我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.13,0:23:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拥有 不想忘却的记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:14.13,BIGSUB,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(308,243)\fn方正隶变_GBK\1c&HFFFFFF}澄  {\1c&H000000}色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:42.59,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly high, make it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:45.79,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the new world that I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:52.17,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, with my little wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:59.01,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look back to the sorrow I left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:05.31,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my real intention I hide
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:11.77,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you were here, and so just right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:18.20,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Need to be strong enough to swallow my pride
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:23.99,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been looking for my own style
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:30.96,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give it up, here comes the life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:36.96,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Be alive, take it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:40.51,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise to find, yes I will
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:46.60,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining wings filled with wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:49.77,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly high, make it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:53.31,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the new world that I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:59.78,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, so I believe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振翅高飞 翱翔九天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将去往自己所追寻的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终有一日 凭借自己那小小的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫回首 将悲伤留在身后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才是我的真意所在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿君伴我身侧 与我肩并肩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坚强地包容我的自傲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在为自己的风格而上下求索
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫轻言弃 这才是生命的真义所在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活下去 莫放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我坚信 自己必会得到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那满怀希望 熠熠生辉的双翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振翅高飞 翱翔九天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将去往自己所追寻的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终有一日 我坚信